OL,3,CWest End star blinded in one eye after
OL,4,Cunprovoked Beckton road rage attack
OL,6,FA seventies TV star may be blind in
OL,7,Fone eye for the rest of his life,
OL,8,Fafter an unprovoked attacker smashed
OL,9,Fthrough van window into his face.
OL,11,FMike Holoway, who most recently toured
OL,12,Fthe UK in Joseph and his Technicolour
OL,13,FDream coat in spin off show Dreamcoat
OL,14,FStars, may never be able to drive or
OL,15,Fperform in the same way again.
OL,17,FMr Holoway had been sitting in traffic
OL,18,Fon his way to work on December 18,
OL,19,F2024, when he spotted a van being
OL,20,Fdriven erratically.
