OL,4,Cunprovoked Beckton road rage attack
OL,6,FMoments later, the van pulled up next
OL,7,Fto him and a man, who was screaming
OL,8,Fand shouting, tried to open Mr
OL,9,FHoloway's door.
OL,11,FWhen the door would not open, the
OL,12,Fattacker smashed through the window
OL,13,Fwith a metal object.
OL,15,FIt hit Mr Holloway, in the head, and
OL,16,Fthe impact threw him across to the
OL,17,Fpassenger seat.
OL,19,F"I just didn't know what was going on.
OL,20,FI was just completely shocked," he
OL,21,Ftold ITV News London.
