OL,6,FThe attacker then ran back into his
OL,7,Fcar and drove away as the traffic
OL,8,Fstarted moving.
OL,10,FAfter seven hours of tests at an A&E
OL,11,Fin Essex, Mr Holoway was referred to
OL,12,FMoorfields Eye Hospital for surgery to
OL,13,Fsave his eye.
OL,15,FThe Tomorrow People star's eye is
OL,16,Fbeing held in place with six
OL,17,Fstructures, and due to scarring he may
OL,18,Fnever be able to see again.
