OL,3,CWest End star blinded in one eye after
OL,4,Cunprovoked Beckton road rage attack
OL,6,FMr Holoway reported the attack to the
OL,7,Fpolice but officers closed the case
OL,8,Fafter three weeks as, they said, there
OL,9,Fwas not enough evidence to identify
OL,10,Fthe attacker.
OL,12,F"I don't feel safe now. I never used
OL,13,Fto think like that," Mr Holoway said.
OL,15,F"I feel completely let down. I don't
OL,16,Ffeel that it was important enough for
OL,17,Fthem. Not that stealing a handbag or a
OL,18,Fmobile phone isn't bad, but this is
OL,19,Fgrievous bodily harm.
