OL,3,CWest End star blinded in one eye after
OL,4,Cunprovoked Beckton road rage attack
OL,6,F"I've lost my sight, it's affected me
OL,7,Fmentally, it's upset my whole
OL,8,Fequilibrium as a human being. On day
OL,9,Fto day, on work, on everything. And
OL,10,Fhe's still out there, just beggars
OL,11,Fbelief."
OL,13,FThe Metropolitan Police said: "We are
OL,14,Faware and share his frustration that
OL,15,Fno one has been held responsible for
OL,16,Fthe attack and will review the details
OL,17,Fof this investigation to ensure there
OL,18,Fis no other evidence that can be
OL,19,Fexplored.
